I recall the first time I met Maya.  We were at a party at Jan Scruggs' house and she was eating something that looked like a Vienna Sausage.<br><br>
Strange, I thought for one would suspect that a beautiful African-American artisit would be a vegatarian, or at least limit herself to fish.<br><br>
We spoke briefly and I was enchanted by her quiet charm.<br><br>
But then William Childs Westmoreland whisked her away from me and I never saw her again.<br><br>
Thanks Maya,<br><br>
Power On!!<br><br>
